Class ResourcesManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • managers.ResourcesManager

  • public class ResourcesManager
extends java.lang.Object
    ResourcesManager.java

    Loads, unloads and saves all resources used in the game. Also contains the engine, camera, activity and vertexBufferObjectManager from the game.

    Version:
    1.0 --/--/----
    Author:
    Davide Teixeria
